{
  "title": "Mildly Spiced Ukrainian Beef Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and comforting Ukrainian dish featuring tender beef, herbal notes, and a hint of pomegranate molasses, perfect for a sick day.",
  "cuisine": "Ukrainian",
